parameters.text:
"How to play:
1. Double Click to cast
2. Click again when fish get hooked
3. Hold your click to reel the fish
4. Fill the bar to finish to get your fish
5. Complete your mission before the time's up(the night clock)
Press H to hide this and S show this"
